{"tid":1287615,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［歷史重演］學生代表又出現","createTime":"2019-07-05T09:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T11:14:20.000Z","uid":114178,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5827ae4129d7042e2e58db1cb52029a7d71b3a","tid":1287615,"uid":114178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:31:54.000Z","msg":"相信各位都對2014年嘅雨傘運動記憶猶新，亦都有目睹過香港人嘅努力係點樣「被代表」，「被騎劫」，而最後敗係大台手上。<br />\n<br />\n今日，歷史似乎又要重演啦：<br />\n<br />\n大學學生會指與特首會面要公開及不追究反修例示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466751-20190705.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466751-20190705.htm&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BMvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=52854ffb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466751-20190705.htm&h=dac638cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466751-20190705.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n各路英雄請小心大台陷阱，今時今日嘅形勢係由諸位志同道合嘅兄弟以血汗堆疊出黎，一眾為香港好嘅無名英雄自發去對抗惡法暴政而黎嘅成果。而家歷史又試開始重演，大台又開始收割社運成果。可以預計嘅係，班人同政府傾掂數就會開始分化，同叫人散水，而諸位辛苦建立嘅就又試毀於一旦，前功盡廢<br />\n<br />\n故此，希望巴打們小心唔好「被代表」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢並唔代表我，只有我先代表我自己</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4a5ead9033621002b6d0643afd300e0bf43e761","tid":1287615,"uid":114178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccc5fc8732a651dbe5603e41700b820b2999bd8","tid":1287615,"uid":51205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:33:00.000Z","msg":"不如你睇番直播人地講咩事講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09369a4ffa3386f4a91017c5d7b99c7e938d8144","tid":1287615,"uid":36797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:33:50.000Z","msg":"人地咪話左唔代表香港人囉"},{"pid":"8f3bea297cbd8754f6f242d10debec00137a4c26","tid":1287615,"uid":114178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09369a4ffa3386f4a91017c5d7b99c7e938d8144","tid":1287615,"uid":36797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:33:50.000Z","msg":"人地咪話左唔代表香港人囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"佢唔係代表所有香港人，而係市民嘅一部份<br />\n<br />\n只要條7婆係咁搵人開會，係咁搵人對話，就形同諮詢<br />\n<br />\n到時佢就可以話已經「諮詢廣大香港市民，而且氣氛良好」<br />\n<br />\n即使佢地唔代表香港人，仍然會為7婆提供脅持民意嘅材料/彈藥"},{"pid":"275cfcde56bb0964492f4ad5e5605bb7941c3794","tid":1287615,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"斷章取義"},{"pid":"0012f09466f79ad593e2e983b24c17ef66b031db","tid":1287615,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"懷疑你無睇記者會"},{"pid":"dcde1f638f3e2a2598af6b3e1bf0d2dea3cf6e19","tid":1287615,"uid":114178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:14:20.000Z","msg":"邊個同佢傾就邊個賦予咗合法性俾777<br />\n<br />\n個運動最好就梗係唔好又被騎劫同搞散啦，不過你可以睇下到時個劇本係唔係咁走，到香港人成功咗嗰日先再屌都未遲"}]}